TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: The source qualifer brings most of the required columns to be populated to target by joining the below tables vwInventoryTransactions WorkOrderSKUs WorkOrders Lots PlantLocations InventoryStatuses InventoryTransactions vwSKURevisions Users ValidInventoryMovements
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_vwInventoryTransactions

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT invTr.WOTransactionID, invTr.RelatedWOTransactionID, invTr.PlantCD, wo.DestinationCD, invTr.WorkOrderSKUID, wo.WorkOrder, wo.ParentWorkOrder, wo.AssortmentParentWO, wo.IsAssortedIND, rTrim(invTr.StyleCD) + ' ' + invTr.ColorCD + ' ' + invTr.AttributeCD + ' ' + invTr.SizeDESC + ' ' + invTr.RevisionCD SKU_Desc, invTr.SKUID AS SKUID, rTrim(sku.StyleCD) + ' ' + sku.ColorCD + ' ' + sku.AttributeCD + ' ' + sku.SizeDESC + ' ' + sku.RevisionCD Assrt_SKU_Desc, CASE WHEN invTrRel.SKUID IS NULL AND wosp.skuid IS NOT NULL THEN wosp.skuid ELSE invTrRel.SKUID END AS Assrt_SKUID, wo.PriorityCD PriorityCD, invTr.ContainerID, invTrRel.ContainerID AS RelContainerID, invTr.MovementID, invTr.QualityCD, invTr.ReasonCD, invTr.StyleCD, invTr.ColorCD, invTr.AttributeCD, invTr.SizeCD, invTr.SizeDESC, invTr.RevisionCD, invTr.FromLocationID, plFrom.LocationName AS FromLocationName, plFrom.LocationCD AS FromLocationCD, plFrom.StatusCD AS FromStatusCD, plFrom.QualityCD AS FromQualityCD, invTr.ToLocationID, plTo.LocationName AS ToLocationName, plTo.LocationCD AS ToLocationCD, plTo.StatusCD AS ToStatusCD, plTo.QualityCD AS ToQualityCD, invTr.Quantity Quantity, CASE WHEN wo.AssortmentParentWO IS NULL THEN 'A' ELSE 'C' END AssortCompInd, invTr.CreatedOnDate CreatedOnDate, invtr.ModifiedOnDate, invTr.TransactionType TransactionType, Usr.FirstName +' '+Usr.LastName CreatedBy, invtr.CreatedByID, Usr2.FirstName +' '+Usr2.LastName ModifiedBy, invtr.ModifiedByID, invTrRel.CommentID, CASE WHEN (fromstatuscd LIKE 'I%') AND tostatuscd IN ('pp', 'pr', 'di', 'mn') THEN 'M1' WHEN invtr.movementid IN (90, 101, 85) THEN 'M2' WHEN invtr.movementid IN (91, 100, 84) THEN 'M3' WHEN fromstatuscd IN ('pp', 'pr', 'di', 'mn') AND tostatuscd LIKE 'I%' THEN 'M4' END AS MovementCateg FROM vwInventoryTransactions invTr WITH (NOLOCK) INNER JOIN WorkOrderSKUs wos WITH (NOLOCK)ON invTr.WorkOrderSKUID = wos.WorkOrderSKUID INNER JOIN WorkOrders wo WITH (NOLOCK) ON wos.WorkOrder = wo.WorkOrder INNER JOIN Lots lt WITH (NOLOCK) ON wo.LotID = lt.LotID LEFT OUTER JOIN WorkOrderSKUs WOSP WITH (NOLOCK) ON wo.AssortmentParentWO = WOSP.Workorder LEFT OUTER JOIN PlantLocations plFrom WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.FromLocationID = plFrom.LocationID LEFT OUTER JOIN PlantLocations plTo WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.ToLocationID = plTo.LocationID LEFT JOIN InventoryStatuses InvfromSts WITH (NOLOCK) ON InvfromSts.StatusCD = plFrom.StatusCD LEFT JOIN InventoryStatuses InvtoSts WITH (NOLOCK) ON InvtoSts.StatusCD = plTo.StatusCD LEFT OUTER JOIN InventoryTransactions invTrRel WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.RelatedWOTransactionID = invTrRel.WOTransactionID LEFT OUTER JOIN vwSKURevisions sku WITH (NOLOCK) ON CASE WHEN invTrRel.SKUID IS NULL AND wosp.skuid IS NOT NULL THEN wosp.skuid ELSE invTrRel.SKUID END = sku.SKUID LEFT JOIN Users Usr WITH (NOLOCK) ON Invtr.CreatedById = Usr.UserId LEFT JOIN Users Usr2 WITH (NOLOCK) ON Invtr.ModifiedById = Usr2.UserId LEFT JOIN ValidInventoryMovements VM WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.MovementID = VM.movementid WHERE invTr.MovementID IN (SELECT DISTINCT movementid FROM validinventorymovements WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE (fromstatuscd LIKE 'I%') AND tostatuscd IN ('pp', 'pr', 'di', 'mn') UNION SELECT DISTINCT movementid FROM validinventorymovements WITH (NOLOCK) WHERE fromstatuscd IN ('pp', 'pr', 'di', 'mn') AND tostatuscd LIKE 'I%' UNION SELECT 90 UNION SELECT 91 UNION SELECT 100 UNION SELECT 12 UNION SELECT 101 UNION SELECT 84 UNION SELECT 85) AND Invtr.CreatedonDate BETWEEN CAST('$$MAX_CREATED_TIME_PRM' AS datetime) AND (CAST('$$MAX_CREATED_TIME_PRM' AS datetime) + 7) UNION ALL SELECT invTr.WOTransactionID, invTr.RelatedWOTransactionID, invTr.PlantCD, wo.DestinationCD, invTr.WorkOrderSKUID, wo.WorkOrder, wo.ParentWorkOrder, wo.AssortmentParentWO, wo.IsAssortedIND, rTrim(invTr.StyleCD) + ' ' + invTr.ColorCD + ' ' + invTr.AttributeCD + ' ' + invTr.SizeDESC + ' ' + invTr.RevisionCD SKU_Desc, invTr.SKUID AS SKUID, rTrim (sku.StyleCD) + ' ' + sku.ColorCD + ' ' + sku.AttributeCD + ' ' + sku.SizeDESC + ' ' + sku.RevisionCD Assrt_SKU_Desc, CASE WHEN invTrRel.SKUID IS NULL AND wosp.skuid IS NOT NULL THEN wosp.skuid ELSE invTrRel.SKUID END AS Assrt_SKUID, wo.PriorityCD PriorityCD, invTr.ContainerID, invTrRel.ContainerID AS RelContainerID, invTr.MovementID, invTr.QualityCD, invTr.ReasonCD, invTr.StyleCD, invTr.ColorCD, invTr.AttributeCD, invTr.SizeCD, invTr.SizeDESC, invTr.RevisionCD, invTr.FromLocationID, plFrom.LocationName AS FromLocationName, plFrom.LocationCD AS FromLocationCD, plFrom.StatusCD AS FromStatusCD, plFrom.QualityCD AS FromQualityCD, invTr.ToLocationID, plTo.LocationName AS ToLocationName, plTo.LocationCD AS ToLocationCD, plTo.StatusCD AS ToStatusCD, plTo.QualityCD AS ToQualityCD, invTr.Quantity Quantity, CASE WHEN wo.AssortmentParentWO IS NULL THEN 'A' ELSE 'C' END AssortCompInd, invTr.CreatedOnDate CreatedOnDate, invtr.ModifiedOnDate, invTr.TransactionType TransactionType, Usr.FirstName +' '+Usr.LastName CreatedBy, invtr.CreatedByID, Usr2.FirstName +' '+Usr2.LastName ModifiedBy, invtr.ModifiedByID, invTrRel.CommentID, CASE WHEN invTr.MovementID = 67 THEN 'M5' ELSE 'M6' END AS MovementCateg FROM vwInventoryTransactions invTr WITH (NOLOCK) LEFT OUTER JOIN WorkOrderSKUs wos WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.WorkOrderSKUID = wos.WorkOrderSKUID LEFT OUTER JOIN WorkOrders wo WITH (NOLOCK) ON wos.WorkOrder = wo.WorkOrder LEFT OUTER JOIN Lots lt WITH (NOLOCK) ON wo.LotID = lt.LotID LEFT OUTER JOIN WorkOrderSKUs WOSP WITH (NOLOCK) ON wo.AssortmentParentWO = WOSP.Workorder LEFT OUTER JOIN PlantLocations plFrom WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.FromLocationID = plFrom.LocationID LEFT OUTER JOIN PlantLocations plTo WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.ToLocationID = plTo.LocationID LEFT JOIN InventoryStatuses InvfromSts WITH (NOLOCK) ON InvfromSts.StatusCD = plFrom.StatusCD LEFT JOIN InventoryStatuses InvtoSts WITH (NOLOCK) ON InvtoSts.StatusCD = plTo.StatusCD LEFT OUTER JOIN InventoryTransactions invTrRel WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.RelatedWOTransactionID = invTrRel.WOTransactionID LEFT OUTER JOIN vwSKURevisions sku WITH (NOLOCK) ON CASE WHEN invTrRel.SKUID IS NULL AND wosp.skuid IS NOT NULL THEN wosp.skuid ELSE invTrRel.SKUID END = sku.SKUID LEFT JOIN Users Usr WITH (NOLOCK) ON Invtr.CreatedById = Usr.UserId LEFT JOIN Users Usr2 WITH (NOLOCK) ON Invtr.ModifiedById = Usr2.UserId LEFT JOIN ValidInventoryMovements VM WITH (NOLOCK) ON invTr.MovementID = VM.movementid WHERE invTr.MovementID NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT movementid FROM validinventorymovements WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE (fromstatuscd LIKE 'I%') AND tostatuscd IN ('pp', 'pr', 'di', 'mn') UNION SELECT DISTINCT movementid FROM validinventorymovements WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE fromstatuscd IN ('pp', 'pr', 'di', 'mn') AND tostatuscd LIKE 'I%' UNION SELECT 12 UNION SELECT 90 UNION SELECT 91 UNION SELECT 100 UNION SELECT 101 UNION SELECT 84 UNION SELECT 85) AND Invtr.CreatedonDate BETWEEN CAST('$$MAX_CREATED_TIME_PRM' AS datetime) AND (CAST('$$MAX_CREATED_TIME_PRM' AS datetime) + 7)
